Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不敢相信！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时代居然连浴室都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 不要太勉强快点上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全身又是血腥味 又是灰尘泥土的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有头发都脏得打结了 我再也受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫做日暮戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本只是一个再平凡不过的国中生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却遇到一个妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬把我拉进了这个战国时代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量不停地涌上来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我的身体也慢慢地恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你身上吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你身上对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我 恶心死了 放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是想要抢到隐藏在我身体里面的四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战国时代桔梗拥有的四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在我的身体里面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我又必须跟觊觎四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让自己变得更强的半妖 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去把变成碎片的四魂之玉收回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是梦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 这绝对不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从食骨之井回到现代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 不要乱叫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉到底怎么了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为戈薇那个时候射出去的破魔箭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射穿了妖怪的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也把妖怪体内的四魂之玉射碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉的碎片已经散落在世界各处了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且根本就不知道是碎成了百片还是千片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过即使只是一个碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果落在妖力很强的妖怪手中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能会酿成很大的灾祸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说起来…不就是我害的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然觉得我也有点责任…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们必须结合彼此的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把四魂之玉的所有碎片都收回来让它恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗？枫老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了我也是觊觎四魂之玉的坏蛋之一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 现在顾不了那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以…我想赶快回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我根本没有那种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且犬夜叉又是个大坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你在啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了我身上还有这串讨厌的咒语念珠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢偷偷摸摸偷看我洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想来偷四魂之玉的碎片对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真了解我 枫老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我不是已经说得很清楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有能看到四魂之玉的戈薇的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上犬夜叉你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能集齐所有的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呀 我不是也说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了找到四魂之玉 我愿意跟这个讨厌的女人合作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你真的这么讨厌我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你那是什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,50年前突然消失的四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又出现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子越来越有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我女儿她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事要先回去了 你们可别吵架哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知廉耻！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是叫你裸体！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是要你穿回那套奇怪的衣服而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我这样像桔梗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她才没关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了 这小子比初中生还幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我们不能再吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然以后怎么可能在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那没什么不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算一个人也会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？意思是没有我也无所谓吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下定决心了 我要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家？喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过我叫戈薇 我的名字不叫「喂」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 臭丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不叫臭丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你别走 臭丫头！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛！你阻止不了我的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个四魂之玉碎片留下来给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先保管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…太不敢相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个犬夜叉 竟然从来都没有叫过我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫大人 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说她突然倒下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她早上还明明很有精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快退下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飘起来了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我出来的枯井
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定能从这里回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骨头…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个枯井在我们这被称作是「食骨之井」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是丢弃妖怪尸体的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要经过几天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些亡骸就会莫名其妙地消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…好像是百足妖怪的尸骨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恶心 我不敢进去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的「发笼」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过光看得到是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那个臭女人我也落个清静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思 你们想和我动手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫做逆发结罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你记不住也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你就快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把四魂之玉弄成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的碎片在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的碎片在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以去死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以去死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:15:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 那个女人怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细看看都是村里的女孩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底想干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道现在还想除掉我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可不会手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你千万不能伤害那些女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么啦 浑身是血的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能换一种说法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能伤害那些女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们想杀我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们好像被什么东西操纵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇呢？戈薇不在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个讨厌的女人已经回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙 我一个人就可以解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝对不能对村里的这些女孩动手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在说什么梦话啊 枫老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是差点被这些人杀了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你还不明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不打倒在背后操纵她们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间听你啰哩叭唆那么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样 犬夜叉 把头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先切断操纵那些女孩的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发？我没看见什么头发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得好好抓住这边的猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 快逃啊！犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操纵这些头发的真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这个样子就算我看不到头发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要用力扯 就可以拉出后面的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 差不多该做个了断了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬、犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有切到肉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为会死掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是普通人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑袋早就落地了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是村里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有新的啊 这样下去就没完没了了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 这里就交给我来应付好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是快点逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快死了就别装酷了 枫老太…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮的银发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我抓紧了 枫老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要小心一点…犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么啊 老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结实的家伙 真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这漂亮的银发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非拿到不可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老太婆 你刚才是不是说看到了头发？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就告诉我 操纵头发的妖怪在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要开玩笑了 我已经伤成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没有受伤 凭我的眼力也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去…找戈薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说那个女人看得到？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的对手 要靠戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有戈薇…你赢不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是枯井下面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我被一个女孩袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就掉进枯井里面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个古井里不是找了很多遍了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是姐姐真的进去了嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是作梦看到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说真的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.29,0:21:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到我的时代了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…你这三天跑到哪去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 你怎么穿着那身衣服啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 好可怕哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 到底发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:21:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这样就差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.32,0:22:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫老太婆 看你这么可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把你埋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我还没死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是先把你藏在这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我记得的话待会会把你挖出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.31,0:22:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要忘记了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你千万别忘记了 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.60,0:22:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 那个臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候到底跑到哪去干什么了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幸福啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:23:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你去哪里 都不会让你跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.65,0:23:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.78,0:23:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}一味地  只知道逞强的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}但是  从那时起我不再茫然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}一定有想要与你分享的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}也有许多想向你倾诉的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}无论是笑容还是泪颜都想呈现给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.84,0:23:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}等待着  将曾经放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.92,0:24:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}机会重新抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.09,0:24:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}我想着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.96,0:24:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}只要如此  便觉得心变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.18,0:24:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}这份渺茫的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.46,0:24:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}无论何时都在祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.41,0:24:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}希望能够传达给你…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.19,0:24:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结罗操纵的头发 犬夜叉根本看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.63,0:24:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能靠蛮力作战的犬夜叉被不断玩弄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.83,0:24:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了解救枫婆婆 得快点解决她
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.63,0:25:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要怎么样才能够打败她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.63,0:25:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉真的能够打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.45,0:25:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自称是不死身的结罗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.52,0:25:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.65,0:25:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结罗一定在什么地方有弱点的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.09,0:25:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.69,0:25:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆发妖魔 结罗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.52,0:25:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请期待
